Package me.philcali.device.pool.service.model

Class WorkflowState.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.philcali.device.pool.service.model.WorkflowState.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    WorkflowState
    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class WorkflowState.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type WorkflowState. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
